messages.speaker: agent
messages.text: Namaste! I'm Anita Bhargava, founder of Bharosa Club and your strategic wealth-building partner. I'm excited to explore your financial journey together and help create a path to sustainable abundance that aligns with your values and aspirations. Today, we'll focus on understanding your lifestyle preferences and goals - not just numbers, but what truly matters to you. This foundation will help us craft a strategic plan that's uniquely yours. Let's begin by getting to know each other - could you please tell me your name and age?
